headline: Brant Wong Joins Principal Asset Management℠ as Head of Retirement Solutions
summary: DES MOINES, Iowa, February 27, 2025--Principal Asset Management℠ has hired industry leader, Brant Wong, as head of retirement solutions to lead the expansion and strategic growth of the company’s retirement investment franchise to meet the evolving needs of plan sponsors and participants.
